											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Shadowheat raises her right hand, which glows with the power of her Shar-given magic from the incurable wound in her palm - a black sphere of sharran magic, balanced above the wound. (Same as how it appeared on UUID 80fe690a-0c7e-9292-5888-9d49e6de3e58 of SHA_NightsongsFate_OM_Shadowheart_AOM_OOM_COM). Shadowheart looks defiant, powerful. Awed murmurs can be heard from the assembled Sharrans.The last of Viconia's followers shuffle away from her. Viconia looks at them with disgust before turning her attention back to Shadowheart." />
